highlights.text: “Encerrado” by El Coyote Y Su Banda Tierra Santa is the highest new entry on Top Songs Mexico at #184.
“Extssy Model” by Junior H has been on Top Songs Mexico the longest, at 1023 days straight.
Fuerza Regida has the most spots on Top Songs Mexico. “TU SANCHO” is the highest at #1.
“La Buena y la Mala” by Banda Tierra Sagrada is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Mexico, up 43 spots at #89.
